# Ground-truth transcriptions: force LF so line endings never vary across platforms.
*.gt.txt text eol=lf

# Line-image crops are small (~8 KB) and write-once — plain git handles them fine,
# no Git LFS needed. Mark them binary so git won't attempt text diffs.
*.png binary

# The trained model is not stored in the repo — it ships as a GitHub Release
# asset (see model/README.md).
